    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用符文制定策略</h2>每个塔都有两种符文特性。将具有相同符文特性的塔配对在一起会给它们带来强大的加成。有8种不同的符文特性，有大量的选择可以搭配。提前计划，以构建最终的组合！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/37c670eacc51365702c31174eaf40de3.poster.avif?t=1745593163\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/37c670eacc51365702c31174eaf40de3.webm?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/37c670eacc51365702c31174eaf40de3.mp4?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地牢生成元素</h2>在Runeroots TD中，没有两次游戏是相同的！敌人路径、资源、特权，甚至你面对的敌人都是随机的。了解你的敌人的弱点，并通过建立完美的防御体系来作出反应，或者在陷入困境时使用你的符文能力！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/c5dbcc4ae08253bf164f1c4eddc554f4.poster.avif?t=1745593163\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/c5dbcc4ae08253bf164f1c4eddc554f4.webm?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/c5dbcc4ae08253bf164f1c4eddc554f4.mp4?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择重要</h2>每次游戏中，你可以选择各种各样的升级。特权会修改特定类型的塔，物品会增强单一的塔，以及特殊的全局修饰符会极大地改变每次游戏的玩法。你是要建造一个超级塔，还是要把特权分散到多个不同的塔上？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/63a555a48356553fb2f13e5b25c7b34d.poster.avif?t=1745593163\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/63a555a48356553fb2f13e5b25c7b34d.webm?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/63a555a48356553fb2f13e5b25c7b34d.mp4?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重建你的家园</h2>随着游戏的进行，你的城镇会逐渐升级！城镇会随时间推移演变，并解锁用于下一次游戏的新功能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/df5024eeee16e0e67d1ec2f5aa792d75.poster.avif?t=1745593163\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/df5024eeee16e0e67d1ec2f5aa792d75.webm?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/df5024eeee16e0e67d1ec2f5aa792d75.mp4?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >两种独特的游戏模式</h2>冒险模式让你可以在3个章节中自由选择你的下一步行动。每过5波后，你可以选择你的下一个目的地。你是应该访问一个符文纪念碑以获得符文能量，还是应该去拿一个宝箱？或者去铁匠铺进行塔的升级！<br><br><br>2) 精通模式为你提供了一个庞大的技术树供你不断进步，从而不断发展你的城镇的技术，使你能够走得越来越远！你能挑战多少波？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/fb25ed35b7dd69224049d2d9d81f4c8b.poster.avif?t=1745593163\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/fb25ed35b7dd69224049d2d9d81f4c8b.webm?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393340/extras/fb25ed35b7dd69224049d2d9d81f4c8b.mp4?t=1745593163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
